._3MJoL{background:no-repeat 50%;background-size:contain;height:30px;width:30px}</style><script>var IsApp = /com\.douban\.frodo/.test(navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase())
      if (IsApp) {
        document
          .documentElement
          .setAttribute('data-isapp', '1')
      }

      if (decodeURIComponent(location.search).indexOf('dark_mode=1') >= 0) {
        document
          .documentElement
          .setAttribute('dark-mode', '1')
      }
      function extractVersionFrom(name) {
        var reg = new RegExp(name + "( |/)([0-9.]*)", "i");
        var info = navigator
          .userAgent
          .toLowerCase()
          .match(reg);
        var version = info
          ? info
            .pop()
            .split('.')
            .slice(0, 3)
            .join('.')
          : '';
        return version;
      }
      function getOS() {
        var ua = navigator
          .userAgent
          .toLowerCase();
        var os;
        if (/android/i.test(ua)) {
          os = 'android';
        } else if (/ipad|iphone|ipod/.test(ua)) {
          os = 'ios';
        } else {
          os = 'web';
        }
        return os
      }
      function vCompare(v1, v2) {
        if (!v1 || !v2) {
          return -1
        }
        var v1Parts = v1.split('.'),
          v2Parts = v2.split('.');

        while (v1Parts.length < v2Parts.length) {
          v1Parts.push('0');
        }
        while (v2Parts.length < v1Parts.length) {
          v2Parts.push('0');
        }

        for (var i = 0; i < v1Parts.length; i++) {
          if (parseInt(v1Parts[i]) === parseInt(v2Parts[i])) {
            continue;
          } else if (parseInt(v1Parts[i]) > parseInt(v2Parts[i])) {
            return 1;
          } else if (parseInt(v1Parts[i]) < parseInt(v2Parts[i])) {
            return -1;
          } else {
            throw new Error('Oops...Unbelievable error! We can only compare numerically!')
          }
        }

        return 0;
      }
      var IsCustomSchema = IsApp && vCompare(extractVersionFrom('rexxar'), '1.2.200') >= 0 && getOS() === 'ios' && vCompare(extractVersionFrom('iOS'), '13.4') >= 0
      function replaceRexxarHttp(link) {
        link = IsCustomSchema
          ? link.replace(/^http/, 'rexxar-http')
          : link
        if (IsCustomSchema) {
          var DEV_SCHEMA = window.localStorage && localStorage.DEV_SCHEMA
          if (DEV_SCHEMA && link.indexOf('img') < 0) {
            console.log('replaceRexxarHttp:' + link)
            link = link.replace(/^rexxar-http/, 'http');
            link = link + (
              link.includes('?')
              ? '&'
              : '?').replace('&&', '&') + 'rexxar_http=1'
          }
        }
        return link
      }
      if (IsCustomSchema) {
        document
          .documentElement
          .setAttribute('data-is-custom-schema', '1')
      }</script>

          if (msg.indexOf('Script error') >= 0) {
            // iOS 5.25.0 才为local file加上跨域支持，https://github.com/douban/rexxar-ios/pull/98
            // ?以需要等iOS 5.25.0 以下没有大量用户的时候，才可以给vendor文件加上crossorigin='anonymous'

            return

data-cs-src-attr="innerHTML"></script><script>(function () {

          var srcEls = document.querySelectorAll('[data-cs-src]')
          function loadFile(i) {
            var srcEl = srcEls[i]
            if (!srcEl) {
              return
            }
            var src = srcEl.getAttribute('data-cs-src')
            if (src[0] === '/') {
              src = location.origin + src
            }
            var srcAttr = srcEl.getAttribute('data-cs-src-attr') || 'src'
            if (srcAttr === 'innerHTML') {
              eval(src)
            } else {
              srcEl[srcAttr] = replaceRexxarHttp(src)
            }

            srcEl.removeAttribute('data-cs-src')
            if (srcEl.tagName === 'SCRIPT' && srcAttr === 'src') {
              srcEl.addEventListener('load', function () {
                loadFile(i + 1)
              })
            } else {
              loadFile(i + 1)
            }
          }
          loadFile(0)
        })()</script>

        </div>

        (function(){
            var site_list = window.white_site_list || new RegExp ([
                '^https?://(.+\\.douban\\.com',
                '|web[0-9]?\\.qq\\.com',
                '|hao\\.qq\\.com',
                '|(hao\\.)*360\\.cn',
                '|so\\.com',
                '|www\\.soso\\.com',
                '|(www\\.)?growingio\\.com',
                '|m-douban-com\\.mipcdn\\.com',
                '|.+\\.baidu\\.com',
                ')(\\:[\\d]+)?/'
            ].join(''));
            if (self !== top && document.referrer.search(site_list) === -1) {
                top.location = self.location;
            }
        })();
